⏰ Bootstrap Styled Clock:

A real-time digital clock built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap. It displays the current time with date formatting and a stylish UI.

🌟 Features
✅ Live Digital Clock – Updates every second.
✅ Date Display – Shows the full date with the weekday, month, and year.
✅ Bootstrap Styling – Modern and responsive design.
✅ Navbar with Navigation – Includes a styled Bootstrap navbar.
✅ Smooth UI Enhancements – Hover effects, gradients, and animations.

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5 – Structure
CSS3 & Bootstrap 5 – Styling & responsiveness
JavaScript – Time and date functionality

🚀 Getting Started
1️⃣ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/bootstrap-clock.git
cd bootstrap-clock
2️⃣ Open index.html in a browser
That's it! The clock will start displaying the current time dynamically.

🎨 Customization
Modify the background colors and gradients in the <style> section.
Update the font size or styles for a personalized look.
🤝 Contributing
Want to enhance this project? Feel free to fork the repo and submit a pull request.
